(Abstract) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 628 Tm
(Person segmentation is useful in image editing, human-centered vision, and background) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 614 Tm
(removal tasks, but final mask boundaries are often unstable around hair, clothing, shadows,) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 600 Tm
(and complex backgrounds. This project studies a practical multi-model pipeline for improving) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 586 Tm
(person boundary segmentation without training a new neural network. The workflow combines) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 572 Tm
(YOLO-based person localization, SAM-based mask generation, Canny edge detection, edge-based) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 558 Tm
(morphological refinement, and GrabCut foreground refinement.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 544 Tm
() Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 530 Tm
(Method Summary) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 516 Tm
(Baseline v1: automatic SAM mask generation with Canny edge scoring and GrabCut.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 502 Tm
(Proposed v6: YOLO person detection creates an automatic SAM box prompt. The resulting mask) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 488 Tm
(is refined by Canny-guided edge refinement and GrabCut.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 474 Tm
