/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 446 Tm
(The formal test set contains 12 selected person images from 34 uploaded photos. Six) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 432 Tm
(automatic versions were batch-tested. Manual box or point prompt versions were prepared but) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 418 Tm
(skipped in the formal batch because manual prompt annotations were not included.) Tj
